    &amp;lt;br /&amp;gt; &amp;lt;ul&amp;gt;&amp;lt;li&amp;gt; fetch his food today &amp;lt;/li&amp;gt;&amp;lt;li&amp;gt; talk to the blacksmith &amp;lt;/li&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/ul&amp;gt;

